      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/untitled-5298_3.jpg",
        "float_quote": "\"Sovereignty is not a title you perform; it is the unshakeable foundation of your original design.\"   — Nancy Vuu",
        "eyebrow": "The Heritage",
        "title_line_1": "A Legacy of",
        "title_italic": "Real Transformation",
        "body": "My journey—from arriving as a refugee to the global stages of fashion—taught me that true style is more than a look; it’s a foundation. From the red carpets of Cannes to the boardrooms of industry leaders, I’ve seen that when your identity is clear, your influence is unshakeable. This isn't just about clothing; it’s about aligning who you are with how the world sees you. We don't just dress the leader; we strengthen the person behind the title.",
